HMV Lenders Near Hiring Advisers Before Strategy Talks, Sky Says

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-02-23T12:39:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-23/hmv-lenders-near-hiring-advisers-before-strategy-talks-sky-says.html
  HMV Group Plc ’s creditors, including
Lloyds Banking Group Plc and  Royal Bank of Scotland Group Plc ,
are likely to appoint advisers by the end of the week to help
them with negotiations about the company’s strategy, Sky News
reported on its website, without attribution.   Deloitte LLP and PricewaterhouseCoopers LLP are among the
firms being considered, Sky said, without saying where it got
the information. The talks are due to take place next month, Sky
said.  For Related News and Information:  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at   ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 